content: Yes Claude! It isn't done yet though, still needs to be deployed and all transcripts run through. We were about to do that and then I got rate limited for another 6 hours. So upsetting. Anyway, it seems like everything is going according to plan. Do you remember the guidance you gave for transcript processing, like what is he looking for? Do you think that will be a one shot thing or is there the ability to take multiple passes through to incorporate learnings along the way?
